isInner": false}, {"id": "c19e7f9", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "e453898", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container showcase\">\n<div class=\"showcase-text\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Everything You Need</span>\n<h2>Your complete client delivery platform.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p>One clean, modern dashboard to run your entire client delivery \u2014 from branding and galleries to video, sharing, automated emails, print sales and insights. Nothing you don't need.</p>\n<ul class=\"featurelist\">\n<li><b>Client galleries</b> \u2014 unlimited, branded, organised in folders.</li>\n<li><b>Video streaming</b> \u2014 smooth playback on any device.</li>\n<li><b>Album &amp; print sales</b> \u2014 extra revenue, built in.</li>\n<li><b>Guest uploads</b> \u2014 every moment in one place.</li>\n<li><b>Automated emails</b> \u2014 sent from your own address.</li>\n<li><b>Activity tracking</b> \u2014 see engagement at a glance.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"Wedding photography client gallery delivered with StudioApp\" height=\"800\" loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610759862400-de105ccacdea?q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" style=\"height:auto\" width=\"1200\"/></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "e2d1c89", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "d01d2c3", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Feature Highlights</span>\n<h2>Beautiful delivery, from upload to download.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"1.5\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><path d=\"M3 15l4-4 3 3 4-5 7 7\"></path><circle cx=\"8.5\" cy=\"8.5\" r=\"1.4\"></circle></svg><h3>Client galleries</h3><p>Create unlimited branded galleries (within your plan), organise them into folders, save reusable templates and set beautiful cover images.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" width=\"20\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\"></rect><path d=\"M10 9l5 3-5 3z\"></path></svg><h3>Video streaming</h3><p>Upload your films straight into a gallery. StudioApp creates web-optimised versions that stream smoothly to couples on any device.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M4 4h16v13H4z\"></path><path d=\"M4 9h16M8 20h8\"></path></svg><h3>Album &amp; print sales</h3><p>Let clients order prints directly from their gallery, then receive and manage every incoming order in one place \u2014 extra revenue, built in.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 15V3m0 0L8 7m4-4l4 4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2\"></path></svg><h3>Guest uploads</h3><p>Turn on guest-upload mode so friends and family can add their own photos and videos to the gallery \u2014 every moment, in one place.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"2\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"5\"></rect><path d=\"M3 7l9 6 9-6\"></path></svg><h3>Automated emails</h3><p>Send a branded \u2018your gallery is ready\u2019 email from your own address, broadcast to all clients, and auto-remind them before a gallery closes.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M3 3v18h18\"></path><path d=\"M7 14l3-3 3 3 5-6\"></path></svg><h3>Activity tracking</h3><p>See engagement on every gallery and track your plan usage \u2014 galleries used versus your allowance \u2014 so you always stay in control.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "a7646f2", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "2b226a1", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container showcase rev\">\n<div class=\"showcase-text\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Your Branding</span>\n<h2>Make it unmistakably yours.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p>Every gallery, client page and email carries your studio\u2019s identity \u2014 so couples only ever see <em>your</em> brand, never ours.</p>\n<ul class=\"featurelist\">\n<li><b>Your logo</b> across galleries and emails.</li>\n<li><b>Studio name &amp; tagline</b> set once.</li>\n<li><b>Accent colour</b> to match your brand.</li>\n<li><b>Branded share links</b> with the couple\u2019s names.</li>\n<li><b>Your sending email</b> (SMTP) for on-brand comms.</li>\n<li><b>QR codes</b> \u2014 instant, downloadable PDFs.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"Elegant branded wedding gallery on StudioApp\" height=\"733\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1575876402495-fe202e1d3732?q=75&amp;w=1100&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" style=\"height:auto\" width=\"1100\"/></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "c6fe265", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "6511edd", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Compatible File Formats</span>\n<h2>Deliver photos &amp; video in stunning quality.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-2\">\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Photos</h3><p>Upload and deliver in beautiful quality: <b>JPEG, PNG, GIF, TIFF</b>, plus WebP and BMP.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Videos</h3><p>Smooth streaming and high quality: <b>MP4, MOV</b>, plus AVI, MKV, WebM and MTS.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "c6f1609", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "