ry.uk/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Start Free Trial</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"plan\">\n<span class=\"tag\">Studio</span>\n<h3>Studio</h3>\n<div class=\"price\">\u00a365 <small>/ month</small></div>\n<p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:.2rem 0 0\">For studios and high-volume photographers.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>60 active galleries</li>\n<li>Unlimited storage</li>\n<li>Video uploads up to 50GB per file</li>\n<li>Custom branding</li>\n<li>Guest uploads</li>\n<li>Activity tracking</li>\n<li>Free SSL, backups &amp; updates</li>\n</ul>\n<a class=\"btn btn-gold\" data-testid=\"plan-studio-btn\" href=\"https://studioappgallery.uk/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Start Free Trial</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container center\" style=\"margin-top:34px\">\n<p class=\"muted\">All plans include a free 7-day trial. No credit card required \u00b7 cancel anytime.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "5f1fb8a", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "9076748", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Testimonials</span>\n<h2>Loved by photographers. Adored by couples.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><p style=\"color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:.4rem\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</p><p style=\"font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--char)\">\u201cWe\u2019ve watched the slideshow five times already. It brought back every emotion from the day.\u201d</p><p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase\">Happy Couple</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><p style=\"color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:.4rem\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</p><p style=\"font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--char)\">\u201cEverything was so easy to download. All our friends and family loved adding their own photos too.\u201d</p><p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase\">Bride &amp; Groom</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><p style=\"color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:.4rem\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</p><p style=\"font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--char)\">\u201cChoosing our album online was brilliant \u2014 so simple and really fun to do together.\u201d</p><p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase\">Newlyweds</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "dc13016", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "4068fc0", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Common Questions</span>\n<h2>Client gallery software FAQs</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container faq\">\n<details open=\"\"><summary>What is client gallery software, and how does StudioApp help photographers?</summary><p>Client gallery software is where you upload, present and deliver a shoot to your clients online. StudioApp gives wedding and portrait photographers beautiful branded galleries, smooth video streaming, guest uploads, automated emails and print sales \u2014 all from one dashboard.</p></details>\n<details><summary>How do I deliver wedding photos and video to my couples?</summary><p>You upload your images and films into a branded gallery, then share a single link (or QR code). Your couple can view, favourite, download and share their photos and watch their film stream smoothly on any device.</p></details>\n<details><summary>Can wedding guests upload their own photos?</summary><p>Yes. Turn on guest uploads and friends and family can add their own photos and videos straight into the gallery, so every moment from the day ends up in one place.</p></details>\n<details><summary>How much does StudioApp cost?</summary><p>Plans start at \u00a315 a month for Starter, \u00a335 for Professional and \u00a365 for Studio. Every plan includes unlimited storage, custom branding, guest uploads and activity tracking.</p></details>\n<details><summary>Is there a free trial?</summary><p>Yes \u2014 there's a free 7-day trial with no credit card required, so you can set up your studio and create your first gallery before you commit.</p></details>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "d271476", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "d178172", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"cta-band\">